## Quick Reference: Existing Examples to Use as Templates

### View Components

| Example | Category | Key Features |
|---------|----------|-------------|
| **calculator** | Interactive utility | Local state, no API calls, simple API (`clear`, `getResult`) |
| **contact-table** | CRUD table | DataPage query, create form, filtering, pagination |
| **root-cause-list** | Display-only table | Read-only, auto-refresh interval, status badges |
| **root-cause-create** | Create form | Record creation, form validation, reset |
| **pir-table** | List with drill-down | DataPage query, filtering, pagination, navigation to detail view |
| **pir-create** | Create form | Complex form, field validation (length, required), cancel button |
| **pir-details** | Detail view | GET by ID, inline edit mode, URL param reading |
| **ticket-kanban-board** | Kanban board | Multi-column layout, per-column queries, multi-field filtering |

### Java Services

| Example | Type | Key Features |
|---------|------|-------------|
| **HelloTestActivity** | Process activity | Simplest example — string in, string out |
| **CalculatorProcessActivity** | Process activity | Multiple inputs, operation routing, response DTO |
| **RecordDefReaderActivity** | Process activity | Record definition metadata, markdown table output |
| **RecordQueryProcessorActivity** | Process activity | Generic query, configurable fields, pagination, markdown table |
| **TicketListProcessActivity** | Process activity | ITSM-specific query, hardcoded record def, markdown table |
| **IncidentFetcherProcessActivity** | Process activity | Single record lookup by ID |
| **ServiceImpactFetcherProcessActivity** | Process activity | Multi-step chained lookup across record definitions |
